      "id": "E:note:row643550:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "87 yo male who presented on [**12-4**]  w/ NSTEMI, acute on chronic    diastolic",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row643550#s1",
      "text": "87 yo male who presented on [**12-4**]  w/ NSTEMI, acute on chronic    diastolic CHF exacerbation & anemia d/t GIB."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row643550:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "NSTEMI was medically    managed.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row643550#s2",
      "text": "NSTEMI was medically    managed."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row643550:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Diuresed on Lasix gtt  & tnsf w/ prbc.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row643550#s3",
      "text": "Diuresed on Lasix gtt  & tnsf w/ prbc."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row643550:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Stable & called out to    floor [**12-9**].",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row643550#s4",
      "text": "Stable & called out to    floor [**12-9**]."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row643550:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Triggered back [**12-11**] prior to scheduled endoscopy for    changes in MS, fe",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row643550#s5",
      "text": "Triggered back [**12-11**] prior to scheduled endoscopy for    changes in MS, fevers (104 pr) ^ wbc 22 (13.4) ^ loose stools (ob+)."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row643550:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Prob C-diff, 1^st sample ([**12-12**]) is positive, started on iv flagyl    (van",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row643550#s6",
      "text": "Prob C-diff, 1^st sample ([**12-12**]) is positive, started on iv flagyl    (vanco/zosyn) Pt also in/out of rapid AF, being successfully tx w/ iv    lopressor q4."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row643550:7",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "MS has improved, now alert, responds to vocal & follows    commands.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row643550#s7",
      "text": "MS has improved, now alert, responds to vocal & follows    commands."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row643550:8",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Conts w/ low grade fevers (99.4-7ax), Cre 2.6 (baseline).",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row643550#s8",
      "text": "Conts w/ low grade fevers (99.4-7ax), Cre 2.6 (baseline)."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row643550:9",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "ECHO done showed no vegetations/ dry, has iv fluids infusing    Gastrointestinal",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row643550#s9",
      "text": "ECHO done showed no vegetations/ dry, has iv fluids infusing    Gastrointestinal bleed, upper (Melena, GI Bleed, GIB)    Assessment:    Hct 31.6 this am down from 34.3 [**12-12**], multiple stools, brown, loose,    Action:    Guiac stool, follow hct    Response:    Ob+    Plan:    Mon;itor hct, s/s bleeding, guiac stool    Renal failure, acute (Acute renal failure, ARF)    Assessment:    Cr ^ 3.0 from 2.6 [**12-13**], u/o began trending down mid day    Action:     started on ns 125cc/hr    Response:    u/o improving    Plan:    Follow renal fx    C. difficile infection (C Diff, Cdiff Colitis, Clostridium Difficile)    Assessment:    Multiple sm-med loose brn stool, tm 100.2., abd increasingly  distended    and tender    Action:    Flagyl d/c, zosyn d/c, vancomycin changed from iv to po, KUB done, plan    for ct, pt taking baracat, starting at    1700    Response:    Cont stooling, low grade temp    Plan:    Monitor temp, stool, abdominal assessment, CT scan this eve"
    }
  ],
